description	"501st Clone Tactician

^2Weaponry:
- DC-17 Blaster Pistol (1)
- DC-15A Clone Rifle (2)
-- 6 Explosive Rounds
- 9 Tracking Darts ^3[CS2]

^6Inventory:
- Portable Shield
- Ammo Dispenser

^8Attributes:
- Advanced Mental Training (Mind Trick Immunity)
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]

Clone Tacticians were invariably assigned to squads when engaging in large operations, and filled a vital support role for the more combat focused troops."